Package swen221.tetris.tetromino

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Tetromino
    An abstract representation of a tetromino which provides various operations for manipulating them, such as rotation and translation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTetromino
    Provides a base implementation from which all concrete tetromino's extend.
    ActiveTetromino
    Represents a tetromino which has not yet been placed on the board.
    I_Tetromino
    I is the 'bar'.
    J_Tetromino
    The "J" tetromino.
    L_Tetromino
    The "L" tetromino.
    O_Tetromino
    The "O" tetromino.
    S_Tetromino
    The "S" tetromino.
    StickyTetromino
    Represents a tetromino which can only perform one rotation operation.
    T_Tetromino
    The "T" tetromino.
    Z_Tetromino
    The "Z" tetromino.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Tetromino.Color
    Represents the colour of a cell on the tetris board.
    Tetromino.Orientation
    The orientation of a tetromino determines the direction in which it is facing.
